ctx: intros l y z H1 H2.
exceptions.exn: In environment orig_base_params : BaseParams one_node_params : OneNodeParams orig_base_params raft_params : RaftParams orig_base_params a : nat l : list nat y, z : nat H1 : forall x : nat, In x (a :: l) -> y <= x H2 : y <= z IHl : (forall x : nat, In x l -> y <= x) -> y <= fold_left Init.Nat.max l z Unable to unify "y <= fold_left Init.Nat.max l z" with "y <= fold_left Init.Nat.max l (Init.Nat.max z a)".

original: intros l y z H1 H2. induction l. - simpl. apply H2. - simpl. apply IHl. + intros x H3. apply H1. * simpl in H3. destruct H3. { subst. apply Nat.le_max_l. } { apply H3. } + apply Nat.le_max_r.
